x4freetext: Cross sections of the (n,p) and (n,alpha) reactions
Thin gold foil was bombarded with a beam containing
deuterons and tritons. Neutron beam was constant with
accuracy 5-10% for 5-6 hr of continuous irradiation.
Radiochemical purity was checked also by measuring
gamma spectra with a single-crystal spectrometer.
